# Global git excludes (core.excludesFile)
#
# Personal-to-this-machine ignores. Things that should NEVER appear in any
# project's tracked .gitignore go here. Build outputs, language ecosystems,
# and framework artifacts belong in per-project .gitignore — not here.
#
# Patterns are gitignore-syntax. Trailing slash = directory only.

# ─── macOS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
.fseventsd

# ─── Editor swap / backup files ─────────────────────────────────────────────
*~
*.bak
*.orig
*.swp
*.swo
*.swn

# ─── Vim / Neovim personal artifacts ────────────────────────────────────────
# (project-shared nvim configs like .nvim.lua should be in project .gitignore)
.netrwhist
Session.vim
.vim/.netrwhist

# ─── JetBrains personal workspace ───────────────────────────────────────────
# (.idea/ itself is often shared — only personal subfiles ignored globally)
**/.idea/workspace.xml
**/.idea/tasks.xml
**/.idea/usage.statistics.xml
**/.idea/shelf/

# ─── ctags / cscope ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
tags
TAGS
cscope.*

# ─── direnv local override ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
.envrc.local

# ─── Personal AI / agent tooling ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Local-only state from agent CLIs. Should never be committed by anyone.
**/.claude/
**/.gsd/
**/.zambo/
**/.opencode/
**/.aider*
**/.cursor/
